    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">About This Project</h2>
    <p class="text-center mb-3">
      This weather application is a real-time web service that allows users to check the weather for any city around the world. It is built with <strong>Node.js</strong> and <strong>Express.js</strong> as the backend, while <strong>EJS</strong> is used for dynamic templating to render the weather data. The frontend is styled using <strong>HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap, and custom CSS</strong> to provide a clean and responsive user interface for users to interact with.
    </p>

    <p class="text-center mb-3">
